 ’n Inskrywingsvormpie sal in die koerant verskyn wat ingevul en by die Middelburg Observer kantore in Meyerstraat ingehandig moet word. Daar sal weekliks ’n gelukkige wenner getrek word. Logo’s verskyn weekliks in meer as een advertensie in die blad. Alle wenners sal gekontak word. • Middelburg Observer readers stand a chance to win a R200 voucher from Café Barista over the next four weeks by simply looking for the café’s hidden logo in advertisments published in the paper. An entryform which appears in the paper, must be filled with the correct answers and handed in at the Middelburg Observer offices in Meyer Street. A weekly lucky winner will be drawn each week. The logo is hidden in more than one advertisment in the paper. Winners will be drawn and notified by the Middelburg Observer.  Add us on WhatsApp for regular news updates. Save the Middelburg Observer standby number 072 248 3855 on your phone and send a WhatsApp message with the words “Add me” to receive news links.